subject: Hockey, Ice
lead_paragraph: J. P. Dumont's floater from the right circle 5 minutes 5 seconds into overtime gave the Sabres a 3-2 victory over the Ottawa Senators and a 3-0 lead in their best-of-seven Eastern Conference semifinal series.
